examples.en: I was met by the police in the person of Sergeant Black.

examples.en: At that moment he came face to face with Sergeant Burke.

examples.en: The sergeant was whining about how hard he had been forced to work recently.

examples.en: He transferred to Southwest Area in 1986, where he was upgraded to Senior Sergeant.

examples.en: The drill sergeant demanded complete and unquestioning obedience from the recruits.

examples.en: I sent for the sergeant of the platoon both men were in and asked him to try to find out discreetly what lay behind this.
examples.ru: Я послал за сержантом взвода, в котором оба они состояли, и попросил его осторожно выяснить, что же за этим стоит.
